  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚗 DRIFTHUB: Where Driving Meets Fun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DRIFTHUB offers a fun and dynamic experience for driving and simulation enthusiasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're playing solo or with friends, this game provides more than just driving—it’s a full entertainment experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔧 Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customization & Building:</strong> Customize your vehicles however you like and build structures in the environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fun with Friends:</strong> Invite your friends and enjoy exciting moments together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expansive Maps:</strong> Explore 7 different maps, each with a unique atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Continuous Updates:</strong> Free updates bring new vehicles and content regularly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-Based Driving:</strong> A realistic physics engine makes your driving experience even more enjoyable. (Steam Link)</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Player:</strong> Enjoy the driving experience on your own.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer:</strong> Play online or locally with friends for shared fun.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LAN Support:</strong> Play together on the same network.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛠️ Ongoing Development</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed by Mevlüt Kart, DRIFTHUB is regularly updated based on player feedback, continuously adding new content. (Steam Link)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DRIFTHUB stands out as a driving and simulation game that offers a fresh perspective. With multiple maps, vehicle customization, and constant updates, this experience is not to be missed!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚗 DRIFTHUB: Where Driving Meets Fun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DRIFTHUB offers a fun and dynamic experience for driving and simulation enthusiasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're playing solo or with friends, this game provides more than just driving—it’s a full entertainment experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔧 Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customization & Building:</strong> Customize your vehicles however you like and build structures in the environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fun with Friends:</strong> Invite your friends and enjoy exciting moments together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expansive Maps:</strong> Explore 7 different maps, each with a unique atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Continuous Updates:</strong> Free updates bring new vehicles and content regularly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-Based Driving:</strong> A realistic physics engine makes your driving experience even more enjoyable. (Steam Link)</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Player:</strong> Enjoy the driving experience on your own.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer:</strong> Play online or locally with friends for shared fun.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LAN Support:</strong> Play together on the same network.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛠️ Ongoing Development</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed by Mevlüt Kart, DRIFTHUB is regularly updated based on player feedback, continuously adding new content. (Steam Link)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DRIFTHUB stands out as a driving and simulation game that offers a fresh perspective. With multiple maps, vehicle customization, and constant updates, this experience is not to be missed!</p>",
